'''俄罗斯思想'''（{{lang-ru|Русская идея}}）是一组表达了[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]民族以及整个俄罗斯国家的历史独特性、特殊使命和全球宗旨的概念。<ref>[https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1177/1354066109356840 Tsygankov, Andrei P. “National Ideology and IR Theory: Three Incarnations of the ‘Russian Idea.’” European Journal of International Relations, vol. 16, no. 4, Dec. 2010, pp. 663–686]</ref> 在该思想在[[苏联解体|苏联解体]]及随之而来的精神缺失后产生，因此与当代俄罗斯具有特殊关联。<ref>[https://www.jstor.org/stable/4211303?seq=1 Aizlewood, Robin. “The Return of the 'Russian Idea' in Publications, 1988-91.” The Slavonic and East European Review, vol. 71, no. 3, 1993, pp. 490–499.]</ref>

